options.panelConfig:
---
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# YAML Aliases to simplify maintenance

anchorLinks:
  - link: &grafana-home
      url: "https://grafana.com/"
      params: "time"
      
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# YAML anchors for colors
portLabelColor: &portLabelColor
  thresholdPatterns:
    - {color: "black", pattern: '.*up.*'}
    - {color: "white", pattern: '.*down.*'}

portFillColor: &portFillColor
  thresholdPatterns:
    - {color: "green", pattern: '.*up.*'}
    - {color: "red", pattern: '.*down.*'}

portStrokeColor: &portStrokeColor
  thresholdPatterns:
    - {color: "green", pattern: '.*up.*'}
    - {color: "red", pattern: '.*down.*'}

portRateColor: &portRateColor
  gradientMode: "hue"
  thresholds:
    - {color: "green", level: 0}
    - {color: "red", level: 100000000000}

portRateLabel: &portRateLabel
  separator: "replace"
  units: "bps"
  decimalPoints: 1

#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Panel Config



cellIdPreamble: "cell-"
cells:

  #------------- Interface operational status based colors
  leaf1-eth1/1:
    dataRef: "OPER leaf1 ethernet-1/1"
    labelColor: *portLabelColor
    fillColor: *portFillColor
    strokeColor: *portStrokeColor

  leaf1-eth1/49:
    dataRef: "OPER leaf1 ethernet-1/49"
    labelColor: *portLabelColor
    fillColor: *portFillColor
    strokeColor: *portStrokeColor

  leaf1-eth1/50:
    dataRef: "OPER leaf1 ethernet-1/50"
    labelColor: *portLabelColor
    fillColor: *portFillColor
    strokeColor: *portStrokeColor

  leaf2-eth1/1:
    dataRef: "OPER leaf2 ethernet-1/1"
    labelColor: *portLabelColor
    fillColor: *portFillColor
    strokeColor: *portStrokeColor

  leaf2-eth1/49:
    dataRef: "OPER leaf2 ethernet-1/49"
    labelColor: *portLabelColor
    fillColor: *portFillColor
    strokeColor: *portStrokeColor

  leaf2-eth1/50:
    dataRef: "OPER leaf2 ethernet-1/50"
    labelColor: *portLabelColor
    fillColor: *portFillColor
    strokeColor: *portStrokeColor

  leaf3-eth1/1:
    dataRef: "OPER leaf3 ethernet-1/1"
    labelColor: *portLabelColor
    fillColor: *portFillColor
    strokeColor: *portStrokeColor

  leaf3-eth1/49:
    dataRef: "OPER leaf3 ethernet-1/49"
    labelColor: *portLabelColor
    fillColor: *portFillColor
    strokeColor: *portStrokeColor

  leaf3-eth1/50:
    dataRef: "OPER leaf3 ethernet-1/50"
    labelColor: *portLabelColor
    fillColor: *portFillColor
    strokeColor: *portStrokeColor


  spine1-eth1/1:
    dataRef: "OPER spine1 ethernet-1/1"
    labelColor: *portLabelColor
    fillColor: *portFillColor
    strokeColor: *portStrokeColor

  spine1-eth1/2:
    dataRef: "OPER spine1 ethernet-1/2"
    labelColor: *portLabelColor
    fillColor: *portFillColor
    strokeColor: *portStrokeColor

  spine1-eth1/3:
    dataRef: "OPER spine1 ethernet-1/3"
    labelColor: *portLabelColor
    fillColor: *portFillColor
    strokeColor: *portStrokeColor

  spine2-eth1/1:
    dataRef: "OPER spine2 ethernet-1/1"
    labelColor: *portLabelColor
    fillColor: *portFillColor
    strokeColor: *portStrokeColor

  spine2-eth1/2:
    dataRef: "OPER spine2 ethernet-1/2"
    labelColor: *portLabelColor
    fillColor: *portFillColor
    strokeColor: *portStrokeColor

  spine2-eth1/3:
    dataRef: "OPER spine2 ethernet-1/3"
    labelColor: *portLabelColor
    fillColor: *portFillColor
    strokeColor: *portStrokeColor


  #------------- Link bandwiths
  tx_leaf1-eth1/1:
    dataRef: "TX leaf1 ethernet-1/1"
    label: *portRateLabel
    labelColor: *portRateColor
    fillColor: *portRateColor
    strokeColor: *portRateColor

  tx_leaf1-eth1/49:
    dataRef: "TX leaf1 ethernet-1/49"
    label: *portRateLabel

  tx_leaf2-eth1/1:

  tx_leaf2-eth1/50:

targets.query: SELECT distinct("/srl_nokia-interfaces:interface/oper-state") FROM "srl_if_oper_state" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval), "interface_name"::tag, "source"::tag
